;NAME is what shows in CTRL-ALT-DEL Task list... hmmmm
NAME           Explorer
DESCRIPTION    &#039;Explorer&#039;
EXETYPE        WINDOWS
CODE           PRELOAD FIXED
DATA           PRELOAD FIXED SHARED
HEAPSIZE       2048
STACKSIZE      8096
